<div class="tiled-section">

  <div class="card-group">
    <div class="card image-card">
      <img class="card-img" src="images/beforeBMR.jpg" alt="Child before surgery">
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Need for Eye Care</h2>
        <p class="card-text">Globally, there is a shortage of pediatric ophthalmologists and optometrists. The shortage of adequate
          eye care providers limits access for underserved children who are uninsured or underinsured to receive the health care they
          need to prevent abnormal visual development.</p>
        <p class="card-text">OneSight partnered with Deloitte to conduct an extensive study and determined that 1.1 billion people
          worldwide suffer from vision loss and lack access to vision care. For all of them,
          vision can be restored with a simple pair of glasses.</p>
        <p class="card-text">According to the American Academy of Pediatric Ophthalmology and Strabismus 19 million children
          worldwide are visually impaired and 80% of visual impairment can be prevented or cured.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card image-card">
      <img class="card-img" src="images/afterBMR.jpg" alt="Child after surgery">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-group">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Medical Services</h2>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>Complete eye exams</li>
          <li>Evaluation for glasses</li>
          <li>Diagnosis and treatment of Amblyopia, Strabismus, and other childhood ocular diseases</li>
          <li>Access to glasses</li>
          <li>Eye care education</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card image-card">
      <img class="card-img" src="images/selfie.jpg" alt="Selfie of surgeons">
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Surgical services</h2>
        <ul class="card-text">
          <li>Strabismus (eye crossing or drifting)</li>
          <li>Nasolacrimal duct obstruction (eye tearing)</li>
          <li>Excisional removal of eyelid growths</li>
          <li>Congenital ptosis (droopy eyelid)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="quote-section">
  <h5 class="px-4">Most causes of childhood blindness are preventable if children receive eye care and treatment from a young age.
    Unfortunately many children in developing countries and even the United States do not have access to this
    standard medical care. Our organization is dedicated to preventing blindness and improving vision to children
    in need. Our current efforts are focused in Sonoyta and Puerto Peñasco, Mexico where we run a monthly eye clinic.

    We currently have two major fundraising goals:
    <ol>
      <li class="ps-3">Raising funds to purchase the equipment needed to make eye glasses in Puerto Peñasco</li>
      <li class="ps-3">Raising funds to set up operating rooms and provide surgical care to children who need sight saving procedures</li>
    </ol>
  </h5>
